[/
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%%
%%  general requirements section
%%
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
/]

[section#rand.req.genl
    [:en] General requirements
    [:zh_CN] 一般规定
]

[para]
[:en] Throughout [#rand], where the template parameters are not constrained,
the names of template parameters are used to express type requirements
on an instantiated template [$T]:
[:zh_CN] [#rand] 的通篇中，凡是对模板形参未加约束之处，均用模板形参的名字表达对
已实例化模板 [$T] 的类型要求：

[list]
[item]
[:en] If [`T] has a template type parameter named
[`Sseq], [`URBG], [`Engine], [`RealType], [`IntType], or [`UIntType],
the program is ill-formed if the corresponding template argument is cv-qualified.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`T] 带有名为 [`Sseq]、[`URBG]、[`Engine]、[`RealType]、[`IntType]
或 [`UIntType] 的模板类型形参，若相应的模板实参被 cv 限定，则程序非良构。

[item]
[:en] A template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`Sseq]
shall meet the requirements of seed sequence ([#rand.req.seedseq]).
[:zh_CN] 对应于名为 [`Sseq] 的模板类型形参的模板实参，应当满足种子序列的规定（[#rand.req.seedseq]）。
[item]
[:en] A template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`URBG]
shall meet the requirements of uniform random bit generator ([#rand.req.urng]).
[:zh_CN] 对应于名为 [`URBG] 的模板类型形参的模板实参，应当满足均匀随机位生成器的规定（[#rand.req.urng]）。
[item]
[:en] A template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`Engine]
shall meet the requirements of random number engine ([#rand.req.eng]).
[:zh_CN] 对应于名为 [`Engine] 的模板类型形参的模板实参，应当满足随机数引擎的规定（[#rand.req.eng]）。
[item]
[:en] If a template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`RealType]
is neither a standard floating-point type ([#basic.fundamental]) nor a member of
an [?impldef subset of extended floating-point types that can be used as [`RealType]
template arguments] subset of extended floating-point types, the program is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果对应于名为 [`RealType] 的模板类型形参的模板实参既不是标准浮点类型（[#basic.fundamental]）
也不是[?impldef 可被用作 [`RealType] 模板实参的扩充浮点类型子集]扩充浮点类型子集的成员，则程序非良构。
[item]
[:en] If a template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`IntType]
is neither a standard signed nor a standard unsigned integer type ([#basic.fundamental]),
nor an extended integer type whose width is greater or equal to that of [`char] and
less than or equal to that of [`long long], nor a member of an [?impldef
subset of integer types that can be used as [`IntType] template arguments] subset
of integer types, the program is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果对应于名为 [`IntType] 的模板形参的模板实参既不是标准有符号或标准无符号整数类型（[#basic.fundamental]），
或者宽度大于等于 [`char] 且小于等于 [`long long] 的宽度的扩充整数类型，也不是
[?impldef 可被用作 [`IntType] 模板实参的整数类型子集]整数类型子集的成员，则程序非良构。
[item]
[:en] If a template argument corresponding to a template parameter named [`UIntType]
is neither a standard or extended unsigned integer type whose width is greater or equal to
that of [`short] and less than or equal to that of [`long long], nor a member of an
[?impldef subset of unsigned integer types that can be used as [`UIntType]
template arguments] subset of unsigned integer types, the program is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果对应于名为 [`UIntType] 的模板形参的模板实参既不是宽度大于等于 [`short]
且小于等于 [`long long] 的宽度的标准或扩充无符号整数类型，也不是[?impldef 可被用作
[`UIntType] 模板实参的无符号整数类型子集]无符号整数类型子集的成员，则程序非良构。

[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Throughout [#rand], phrases of the form [=lq][`x] is an iterator of a
specific kind[=rq] shall be interpreted as equivalent to the more formal
requirement that [=lq][`x] is a value of a type meeting the requirements
of the specified iterator type[=rq].
[:zh_CN] [#rand] 的通篇中，形式为“[`x] 为某特定种类的迭代器”的表述应当被理解为
等价于更正式的规定“[`x] 为满足特定迭代器类型之规定的类型的值”。

[para]
[:en] Throughout [#rand], any constructor that can be called with a single
argument and that meets a requirement specified in this subclause shall be
declared [`:key explicit].
[:zh_CN] [#rand] 的通篇中，可以用单个实参进行调用，并且满足本子条款中的规定的
任何构造函数，应当被声明为 [`:key explicit]。
